		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Wondrous Item - Legendary (Requires Attunement by a Sorcerer, Warlock, or Wizard)</em></p><p>This elegant garment is made from exquisite cloth and adorned with runes.</p><p>You gain these benefits while wearing the robe.</p><p><em><strong>Armor.</strong></em> If you aren't wearing armor, your base &amp;reference[Armor Class] is 15 plus your Dexterity modifier.</p><p><em><strong>Magic Resistance.</strong></em> You have Advantage on saving throws against spells and other magical effects.</p><p><em><strong>War Mage.</strong></em> Your spell save DC and spell attack bonus each increase by 2.</p><section><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>The <strong>Archmagi Armor</strong> Active Effect sets your AC and should be disabled if you're still wearing armor.</p><p>The <strong>War Mage</strong> Active Effect automatically increases you spell save and attack bonus increases.</p></section>",
